&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;iframe style=&quot;width: 417px; height: 234px;&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/B-XAoG8A_60?si=kdDgqSPjXbDIL1tg&quot; width=&quot;417&quot; height=&quot;234&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;📣 A bit about the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Butternut Box&#39;s mission is to deliver health and happiness to dogs all over the world with our fresh dog food and extras, delivered directly to customer&#39;s doors on a subscription model. To achieve our amazing growth targets, we are looking for passionate, driven, and fun Brand Ambassadors to join our high-performing sales teams. You will represent us at events, trade shows, and exhibitions across the country, engaging with dog owners and promoting the benefits of feeding fresh. If you love dogs, sales and flexible work - this could be the ideal role for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;❗️️&lt;/strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Driving face to face sales: Engage with potential customers at top-tier events in Bristol and surrounding areas, promoting Butternut Box in an ethical and inspirational manner. Shows include Crufts, Dogfest, Ideal Home Show etc (we go to over 900 a year as a business!).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Educating dog parents: Inform and educate our customer base about the benefits of Butternut Box, ensuring they understand our commitment to high-quality, natural,&amp;nbsp;fresh&amp;nbsp;food.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Building relationships: Develop and maintain strong relationships with customers, fostering trust and loyalty.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Achieving sales targets: Be target-driven, striving to exceed individual and team sales goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;👋 A bit about you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Dog lover: It goes without saying that you must have a genuine affection for dogs and an understanding of their needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Sales enthusiast: A passion for sales and a knack for connecting with people (and their dogs) is very impawtent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Customer focus: We strive to provide the best service possible, so a dedication to helping customers and their dogs is non negotiable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Target-oriented: The more dogs you help, the more you earn - tasty right?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Available on weekends: The majority of our high impact events fall on a weekend, so it&#39;s imperative that you have generally good availability Friday - Sunday.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-bor

