&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Fulfilment General Operator&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Career Step Level:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Step level 1&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps?sca_esv=c702797afd47edb8&amp;amp;rlz=1C1GCCU_enGB1152GB1152&amp;amp;output=search&amp;amp;q=rudies+kitchen&amp;amp;source=lnms&amp;amp;fbs=AIIjpHxU7SXXniUZfeShr2fp4giZ1Y6MJ25_tmWITc7uy4KIehZSPZtq-ywdxHK81a_1UWlQN69SKmEwbxp_WUDdFSSoWKnLZsmnMG2zzoBYr4Zou2mC6_JsVvXi9hLEYkMuzyPnuRxxNdzwIyDUZVVgUR70IAxGA4iylUCVLot7OurUnFEddHJxeKmhlYm5hmlb_15lqm5vlLT9qjn8Sv_OnHTgZCA5sw&amp;amp;entry=mc&amp;amp;ved=1t:200715&amp;amp;ictx=111&quot;&gt;Blyth, Worksop&lt;br&gt;&lt;/a&gt;This is an on-site shift-based role, based in Blyth, Worksop.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours: &lt;/strong&gt;We are pleased to say, this is a full-time permanent contract, you will be working a rolling average of 41 hours per week working on a shift rotation of days and some weekend working. The working shifts days consisting of 7am to 7pm.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;£13.99&lt;/strong&gt; per hour, salary of &lt;strong&gt;£29,921&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;🐾 A bit about us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Butternut, the mission is to deliver health and happiness to dogs and their humans all over the world. In order to do just that, we need a team of forward-thinking, driven people who love dogs as much as we do. And we need some pretty impressive kitchens to make it happen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While Rudie&#39;s Kitchen and Ace&#39;s Pantry in Doncaster remain the heart of our UK operations, we’ve recently taken a massive leap forward with Sam’s Kitchen in Poland, going live in January this year. This expansion is a huge part of our story, allowing us to bring our gently cooked, human-quality meals to even more four-legged friends across Europe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We believe dogs deserve better, and we wouldn&#39;t serve food to them that we wouldn&#39;t be happy to eat ourselves. Butternut has come a long way since Kev &amp;amp; Dave (our co-founders) hand-delivered the first Butternut Box, and with our new international footprint, we are looking for brilliant people to join us for this next chapter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you up for the challenge?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🐕‍🦺&amp;nbsp; &lt;strong&gt;A bit about the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a safe way following all appropriate safety procedures and wearing protective equipment correctly at all times.&lt;/li&gt;
